AgriGuru

Empowering Farmers with AI: Get personalized crop recommendations, weather forecasts, organic farming tips, government schemes, and more—all in one elegant platform.

About the Project

AgriGuru is an innovative AI-powered assistant designed to revolutionize Indian agriculture. Our platform brings together crop recommendations, real-time weather, government schemes, organic tips, satellite insights, and a smart chatbot—all tailored for farmers and agri-enthusiasts.

What Makes AgriGuru Unique?

  • Integrates AI (Gemini) for personalized, region-specific advice
  • Combines satellite data, weather, and expert tips in one place
  • Supports English, Hindi, and Kannada for inclusivity
  • Modern, mobile-friendly, and easy to use

Our Inspiration

Inspired by the resilience and innovation of Indian farmers, AgriGuru aims to bridge the gap between cutting-edge technology and grassroots agriculture. We believe that empowering farmers with timely, actionable insights can transform lives and ensure food security for all.
